metadata.name: I Spy with my Little Eye
metadata.description:
Seeing is multifaceted, that what is seen, must be seen, from multiple points of view.
Hold it up.
Walk around it.
Mull on its multiplicities.
Listen to others who hold it up, walk around it, mull on its multiplicities. 
Resist fixity, finality, single perspectives.

The work use the metaphor of the “EYE” to question what you see, where you saw it and why was it seen?
